{"tid":1818274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"面具下的勇武","createTime":"2020-01-09T18:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T12:50:46.000Z","uid":167042,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"96de52b9c7a4c7523ea2024323735bb9561cf757","tid":1818274,"uid":167042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2upfLKX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2upfLKX.jpg&h=7a74b45e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n面具下嘅勇武只係個同你擦身以過嘅陌生人<br />\n佢地行前一步但呢一步知唔知背負咗幾多嘢？<br />\n家庭？前途？將來？<br />\n<br />\n我知道件事降温咗好多<br />\n我想問大家係咪好攰呀？<br />\n五大訴求係咪算啦？<br />\n咁班比狗拉咗嘅手足係咪就係condom呀？<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以生生性性贏返次 <br />\n班手足真係等緊大家幫佢贏 <br />\n如果今次不了了知 我同大家講你地冇資格講任何民主自由<br />\n你地係害咗7000個手足嘅付出<br />\n啲屍體發現案係真係好彩唔係你身邊人<br />\n<br />\n三罷真係咁難？<br />\n三罷成功我地先有最權令政府屈服嘅一個籌碼<br />\n我講完<br />\n<br />\n大家可以繼續開啲鳩post做返6月前嘅連登"},{"pid":"195c0484cdfc8f44e1bec473831d0acc71b71f53","tid":1818274,"uid":127033,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:44:52.000Z","msg":"成日係街睇下邊個後生仔係勇武手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a11ac9e95f827678d48eaafd4634ca9a2f97c85","tid":1818274,"uid":98993,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:49:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6da732d11685ead07bd2e1d8ce31187407a9e72","tid":1818274,"uid":167042,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"195c0484cdfc8f44e1bec473831d0acc71b71f53","tid":1818274,"uid":127033,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:44:52.000Z","msg":"成日係街睇下邊個後生仔係勇武手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:50:14.000Z","msg":"你估唔到 <br />\n隨時茶餐廳個哥哥仔係手足"},{"pid":"3050dd159c2786f6c38bb2b11d742e17b48a21f4","tid":1818274,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T18:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkg